# Investigating Netflix Movies 🎬

This project explores a dataset of Netflix movies to uncover insights such as:

- How the average movie rating changed over the years
- Which genres are most common on Netflix
- Distribution of movie durations
- Trends over time

## 🔧 Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Jupyter Notebook

## 📁 Files
- `Investigating Netflix Movies.ipynb`: Main analysis notebook
- `netflix_movies.csv`: Dataset used in the project

## 📊 Insights
The project contains various visualizations that help better understand the content available on Netflix, including rating trends, genre distributions, and more.

## 🚀 How to Run
Open the notebook in Jupyter or VS Code and run the cells step by step.

